      detectionLogic: 'Alert when inbound flows from external (non-RFC1918) sources are ACCEPT on management ports (22, 3389, 5985, 445, 135) or database ports (3306, 5432, 1433, 27017, 6379). Any accepted inbound management connection from the internet is critical unless the instance is a designated bastion.',
