      investigationWorkflow: '1. Identify the exposed instance and verify it is not an approved bastion\n2. Check the security group and NACL rules — was this intentional?\n3. Determine when the exposure started (new security group rule?)\n4. Review CloudTrail for the security group modification\n5. Check if any successful authentication occurred via the exposed port\n6. Remediate immediately by restricting the security group',
