      falsePositives: ['Legitimate relative path references in poorly coded applications', 'Security scanning tools during authorized assessments', 'URL rewrite rules that internally use relative paths'],
      tuningGuidance: 'Focus alerting on traversal attempts that receive 200 responses (successful exploitation). Create exceptions for known application paths that legitimately contain relative references. Whitelist authorized scanner IPs.',
