      tuningGuidance: 'Focus on high-volume failures from single IPs. Low-volume failures (1-5) are likely legitimate users. Consider user_agent patterns to distinguish tools from browsers.',
      investigationWorkflow: '1. Check the client_ip and user_agent pattern\n2. Review targeted endpoints — are they high-value (login, checkout)?\n3. Examine bot_score distribution — consistently high confirms automation\n4. Check if any challenges were eventually passed (adaptive tools)\n5. Review volume trend — is it increasing (scaling up attack)?\n6. Consider IP blocking or enhanced challenge difficulty',
