      investigationWorkflow: '1. Identify the new rule_id and its description\n2. Check if this is a new Akamai rule set update\n3. Review targeted hosts and paths — new application deployment?\n4. Examine source IPs — single attacker or distributed?\n5. Assess whether rule action is appropriate (deny vs alert)\n6. Update detection baselines and communication if legitimate new rule',
