      falsePositives: ['Approved emergency access grants with retroactive tickets', 'Automated provisioning from HR systems during role changes', 'Break-glass account activations during incidents'],
      tuningGuidance: 'Integrate with change management API to auto-close alerts with matching tickets. Define organization-specific admin role names. Set highest severity for self-escalation. Monitor for role assignments outside business hours.',
      investigationWorkflow: '1. Identify who performed the role assignment (actor_username)\n2. Determine what admin role was granted and to whom\n3. Check change management system for an approved ticket\n4. Verify if this is a self-escalation (actor == target)\n5. Review the actor account for signs of compromise\n6. If unauthorized, immediately revoke the role and investigate the actor account',
