      investigationWorkflow: '1. Identify the device and its managed/health status\n2. Determine the user and their device enrollment status in MDM\n3. Check if the user has a BYOD exception or is a contractor\n4. Review what application was accessed from the unmanaged device\n5. Check if the device has been seen before or is completely new\n6. If unauthorized, block the device and review data access logs',
