      investigationWorkflow: '1. Map both authentication locations and calculate distance\n2. Verify time between authentications makes travel impossible\n3. Check if either IP is a known VPN or proxy egress\n4. Determine if user has reported travel plans\n5. Review what was accessed from each location\n6. Contact user to verify — if unconfirmed, treat as compromise',
