      tuningGuidance: 'Baseline each user primary factor over 30 days. Only alert on downgrades that persist beyond a single session. Increase severity if combined with other indicators (new location, bypass code request). Monitor for users who permanently switch to weaker factors.',
      investigationWorkflow: '1. Identify the factor change — what was the user normally using vs now?\n2. Check if the stronger factor device is still enrolled and active\n3. Determine if the user requested the change or if it was automatic fallback\n4. Review the source IP and location for consistency\n5. Check for recent SIM swap reports on the user phone number\n6. Contact user to verify intentional factor change',
