      detectionLogic: 'Monitor for IIS substatus codes indicating ASP.NET security events: 500.19 (config error/manipulation), 500.21 (module error), 500.22/500.23 (managed pipeline issues), and request validation failures (indicating XSS/injection blocked by ASP.NET). Also detect ViewState manipulation attempts (MAC validation failures) which are precursors to deserialization attacks.',
