      investigationWorkflow: '1. Identify the specific substatus code and its meaning\n2. Determine if this is a targeted attack or generic scanning\n3. For ViewState errors, check for deserialization attack attempts\n4. For config errors (500.19), verify no unauthorized config changes\n5. Review the full request for exploitation payloads\n6. Check ASP.NET version for known vulnerabilities matching the attack',
