      tuningGuidance: 'Exclude internal IPs and known application source ranges. Allow OPTIONS for known CORS-enabled endpoints. Block TRACE at the server level. Focus on WebDAV methods if WebDAV is disabled. Alert on DELETE/PUT to unexpected paths.',
      investigationWorkflow: '1. Identify the HTTP method used and the target resource\n2. Determine if the source is internal or external\n3. Check if the method is expected for the target application\n4. For WebDAV methods, verify if WebDAV is intentionally enabled\n5. For TRACE, check if cross-site tracing (XST) attack is being attempted\n6. If DELETE/PUT from external, verify no data was modified or removed',
