      investigationWorkflow: '1. Identify source_network_address — is this internal or external?\n2. Determine target_username(s) — single target or multiple accounts?\n3. Check sub_status codes to understand failure reasons (bad password vs account locked)\n4. Look for a successful 4624 following the failures (indicates compromise)\n5. Check if source IP appears in threat intelligence feeds\n6. Verify with account owners and check for account lockouts',
