      requiredFields: ['event_id', 'timestamp', 'computer', 'faulting_application', 'faulting_module', 'faulting_module_path', 'exception_code', 'faulting_process_id'],
      detectionLogic: 'Alert on EventID 1000 where faulting_module_path is outside standard system directories (C:\\Windows\\System32, C:\\Windows\\SysWOW64, C:\\Program Files). Focus on critical processes (svchost.exe, explorer.exe, winlogon.exe, services.exe) loading modules from Temp, AppData, or user-writable locations. Correlate with Sysmon Event 7 for DLL load confirmation.',
