      detectionLogic: 'Alert on Sysmon Event 13 (RegistryEvent SetValue) where target_object contains Run, RunOnce, RunServices, or RunServicesOnce keys under HKLM\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion or HKCU equivalent. Focus on values pointing to executables in temp directories, encoded commands, or unsigned binaries. Correlate with the image (process) performing the modification.',
