      objective: 'Detect creation or connection to named pipes (Sysmon Events 17/18) that match patterns used by known attack tools (Cobalt Strike, PsExec, Mimikatz, Metasploit), which use named pipes for inter-process communication during lateral movement, privilege escalation, and command-and-control.',
      severity: 'Low',
