      name: 'High-Privilege Account on Many Machines',
      objective: 'Detect a single privileged account authenticating to an unusually high number of hosts (10+) via WEF-collected logon events, which may indicate credential compromise with the attacker using the account for widespread reconnaissance or lateral movement across the enterprise.',
