      investigationWorkflow: '1. Identify the affected user and endpoint\n2. Check the WildFire report for malware family and behavior\n3. Determine the delivery vector — web download, email link, or other\n4. Check if the file was executed on the endpoint\n5. Look for lateral movement or C2 activity from the affected host\n6. Initiate endpoint isolation if execution is confirmed',
