      tuningGuidance: 'Build per-user application baselines over 30 days. Exclude commonly adopted new applications organization-wide. Focus on applications capable of large data transfer.',
      investigationWorkflow: '1. Identify the application and its data transfer capabilities\n2. Review the user history — have they ever used this application?\n3. Check transfer volume — is it significant enough for concern?\n4. Look at the destination — where is data being sent?\n5. Correlate with HR data — is this a departing employee?\n6. Review if similar anomalies exist for other users on same team',
