      investigationWorkflow: '1. Identify all active sessions for the user — how many and from where?\n2. Check if devices are different or the same device with IP change\n3. Review login times — did sessions overlap or just transition?\n4. Check if one session shows anomalous geographic origin\n5. Verify with the user if they have multiple active devices\n6. If credential sharing confirmed, enforce password change and review access logs',
