      investigationWorkflow: '1. Compare the certificate CN with the connecting device name\n2. Check certificate expiration — is it expired or about to expire?\n3. Review the gateway policy — why was the anomalous cert accepted?\n4. Check device inventory for the presented certificate CN\n5. Look for other authentication anomalies from the same device\n6. If device spoofing suspected, revoke the certificate and block the device',
