      investigationWorkflow: '1. Identify the contained host and the triggering IOC\n2. Review the IOC details — what malware family or behavior was detected?\n3. Check if the host was patient zero or part of a larger infection\n4. Review the timeline leading up to containment\n5. Determine the scope — are other hosts showing similar IOCs?\n6. Begin incident response: preserve evidence, identify attack vector, assess impact',
