      falsePositives: ['Wireless roaming between access points (expected in WiFi)', 'VM migrations moving virtual MAC addresses between hosts', 'Dual-homed devices with the same MAC on different interfaces'],
      tuningGuidance: 'Exclude wireless MACs from this detection (roaming is normal). Focus on wired 802.1X and MAB events. Set time window based on physical impossibility of moving between locations.',
