      falsePositives: ['Newly provisioned keys not yet added to inventory', 'Partner or vendor keys used for integrations', 'Test keys from development environments'],
      tuningGuidance: 'Maintain an up-to-date key inventory with daily sync. Create a grace period for new keys (24-48 hours). Tag keys by environment (prod/dev/test) for context.',
