      investigationWorkflow: '1. Identify the source and destination IPs\n2. Determine the destination ownership (ASN lookup)\n3. Check if this is a known backup or replication flow\n4. Review the protocol and port for context\n5. Check source host for compromise indicators\n6. Calculate total data volume and assess impact',
