      investigationWorkflow: '1. Identify the scanning source IP\n2. Determine scan type (vertical vs horizontal)\n3. Check if source is a known authorized scanner\n4. Review which ports/hosts responded\n5. Check for follow-up exploitation attempts\n6. Correlate with threat intelligence for source reputation',
