      tuningGuidance: 'Build port-to-application baseline over 14 days. Whitelist known tunneled services. Focus on external-facing ports. Consider application categorization rather than strict mapping.',
      investigationWorkflow: '1. Identify the mismatched application and port\n2. Determine if this is a known legitimate tunneled service\n3. Review the traffic volume and pattern\n4. Check if this is a new occurrence or established\n5. Assess protocol abuse potential\n6. Investigate source host for suspicious software',
